214
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,520
To já vím.

215
00:11:20,890 --> 00:11:22,980
Stačí, když mě jenom povedeš.

216
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:24,230
Á, tady jsou!

217
00:11:24,690 --> 00:11:25,440
To jsou oni!

218
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:33,150
Ale to je jenom děcko!

219
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:33,950
Jo.

220
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:38,700
