222
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:42,620
Vůdkyně Hadou!

223
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:47,670
Promiňte, ale máte domluvenou schůzku?

224
00:11:48,170 --> 00:11:49,000
No... ne...

225
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:50,670
Pak, prosím, odejděte.

226
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:52,510
Mně to nevadí, Winfielde.

227
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,220
A vy jste?

228
